==English==
===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|es|Xochapa}}, from a {{der|en|azc-nah}} language (equivalent to {{cog|nci|xōchitl|t=flower}} + {{m|nci|āpan|t=river}}), calqued from a {{der|en|omq-mxt}} language, e.g. {{noncog|xta|I̱ta Ita|lit=flower river}}.
